'''Vjun tunics''' were extremely expensive garments handwoven on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Vjun/Legends|Vjun]]. [[Count/Legends|Count]] [[Dooku/Legends|Dooku]] owned such a tunic, he had it in his possession sometime before the [[Mission to Jabba's Palace (Clone Wars)/Legends|Mission to Jabba's Palace.]] He also wore it during the [[Battle of Coruscant/Legends|Battle of Coruscant]] prior to the end of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

